data.title: Honesty
data.description: Uprightness of character and action. Has a strong inclination to tollie, steal, or deceive in any way. An active disposition regard for the standards of one's profession, calling, or ition.

data.title: Excellence
data.description: Being good at a good thing. Has the ability to strive to be the best one can be and to do the best thatonecando.

data.title: Responsiblity
data.description: Understands and knows the obligations of his/her duties and able to perform the duties or tasks assigned.

data.title: Respect
data.description: Ability to show appreciation for someone's traits or qualities and treating people with dignity and gratitude. Able to abide with the company's Code of Conduct.

data.title: Ownership
data.description: Displays proactive, solution-oriented, accountable, transparent and commitment in the performance of his/her duties. Displays the abiity to take on challenges.

data.title: Integrity
data.description: Possessing upstanding character traits, work ethics, sound judgement, and loyalty. Consistenctly doing the right thing through words and actions.

data.title: Customer 1st
data.description: Consistently seeking ways to deliver a positive Customer experience by designing and delivering services with the Customer in mind. Able to go above and beyond to deliver exceptional service.
